AddressInfo.Title: Flair Hotel
AddressInfo.AccessComments: In der Tiefgarage des Hotels direkt rechts neben dem Tor die erste Parkbucht. Dort hängt eine 22kW LOLO von The New Motion

GeneralComments: Typ2 connector works fine, but currently only one phase connected (owner reported 3 phases will be connected if there are enough requests, electrician used wrong cable). The Hotel is very nice, good restaurant and the staff is wonderful friendly and höxter town is definitly worth a visit, center in walking distance. current charge level is 4kw, no special card required, parking is 5 € per night, reservation of the charging space is recommended, simply send an email to info@hotel-stadt-hoexter.de with your booking and they will block the space.
